title: Dark Heresy Character Folio in a writable .pdf format
description:
Warhammer 40k Roleplay: Dark Heresy 

-= Dark Heresy Character Folio in a Writable .pdf Format =-


A most useful thing for any dedicated Dark Heresy player with a laptop (or data slate :)). 

Notes:

1) A major typo in the original Folio was corrected (Left Leg was erroneously named as "Left Arm"; copypaste at Black Industries - that's it :)). In this version, this unfortunate blunder is corrected (thanks to Acrobat "stamp" tool).

2) The file is working under for Adobe Acrobat (Reader) v.8+

3) Comments and suggestions are welcome!

Enjoy.
